org.mechio.api.animation

Class Animation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mechio.api.animation.Animation

  • public class Animation
extends Object
    An Animation holds a map of servo IDs and Channel. This also stores the JointParameters corresponding to each Channel.
    Author:
    Matthew Stevenson
